{"product_id":"norrskin-highly-nourishing-face-cream-50ml","title":"NorrSkin Highly Nourishing Face Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNourishes \u0026amp; moisturises, supports hydro lipid barrier in the skin. Soothing effect, prevents skin irritation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBenefits: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVisibly improves skin texture in 14 days (confirmed by clinical tests)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeeply nourishes with power of Niacinamide and Linseed\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrevents skin dryness and dehydration with plant derived squalane\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRich in vitamins and minerals (calcium, magnesium \u0026amp; Zinc)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt reduces the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt soothes skin and prevents irritations\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eSqualane\u003c\/span\u003e protects the skin from water loss. Deeply moisturises the skin, has a mild formula, making it suitable for sensitive skin, regulates production of sebum, has a strong anti-aging effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNiacinamide\u003c\/span\u003e, also knows as Vitamin B3 and strong antioxidant, has a cleaning, detoxifying and brightening properties. Decreases redness and irritations on the skin. Stimulates elasticity.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eLinseed Oil\u003c\/span\u003e is extra-rich, plant-derived source of Omega-3 fatty acids. Provides a nourishing lipid barrier.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e96,3% natural origin ingredients, dermatologically tested.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a small amount of the cream on your face and neck. Gently massage the cream into the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Squalane, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate, Cetearyl Olivate, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Sorbitan Olivate, Cetearyl Alcohol, 1,2-Hexanediol, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Niacinamide, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil, Arginine, Fragaria Vesca Fruit Extract, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Extract, Oryza Sativa Bran Wax, Centella Asiatica Root Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Stearic Acid, Lactic Acid, Parfum, Xanthan Gum, Hydroxyacetophenone, Sodium Phytate, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Linalool, Citronellol, Hexyl Cinnamal.  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNatural Certified | Clean Certified | Vegan Certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eInspired by Hälsingland, Sweden.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNorrSkin plants 1 tree for every product sold.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"bioskina","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49308376498503,"sku":null,"price":35.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/norrskin-highly-nourishing-face-cream-50ml-799906.png?v=1739897345","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/norrskin-highly-nourishing-face-cream-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}